      <title>亚马逊 Ring 推出每月 5 美元的烟雾监测服务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-06/amazon-s-ring-debuts-5-a-month-smoke-monitoring-service-ces</link>
